6:
Now, for the final course... Hachis
Gruyere!
23:
HELLOOOOO, PALPEBRA! Are we all
having a good time?!
27:
What you just witnessed was this
year's opening ceremony!
Sponsored by yours truly... The Guild!
31:
Oh. It was just Guild shenanigans. I
should've expected...
35:
Ahem. And now, ladies and
gentlemen, I am pleased to
announce the moment you've all
been waiting for...
39:
The Valentine's Festival has officially
begun!
45:
Hey, everyone! This sculpture's
edible too, so make sure you grab a
piece!
51:
Phew... I'm sure glad our cover-up
worked.
54:
Palpebrans are quite... unshakable.
But I am glad the festival is saved.
58:
I mean, we're next door neighbors
with the Kaleidoscope. We eat
chaos for breakfast.
69:
Whoooa. This chocolate... It's so
creeeamy...
70: *sigh* I think I hear angels singing...
73:
They can't get enough! Guess all our
hard work paid off, right?
81:
There's still a TON of chocolate left!
Step up, and make the most of this
year's festival!
88:
Good work, gang! We, uh, had some
unexpected difficulties, but we
managed to push through.
91:
And thanks to your cooperation, the
Valentine's festival was a crazy
success!
94:
The guests LOVED your chocolate,
Parfait! You know, maybe that whole
mess with the attack of the living
food art was a sign to get back into
normal cooking.
99:
Okay, I admit that the golem thing
wasn't supposed to happen!
101:
But Lilie, I have my own way of
bringing joy. I hope you can
understand...
105:
Yeah... You know what, Parfait? You
do you.
110:
Hey, guys... I have one last favor to
ask.
114:
I want to see what's out there... Not
just on this world, but on every world
in the sky. I want to take Monster
Cuisine to unimaginable heights!
116: Will you let me join you?
120: We'd be happy to have you.
124:
Heh. I'm not turning down another
chef.
128:
I only ask that we not eat monster
every day. Please.
133:
You will be welcome at Starview
Village.
143:
I am gonna practice so much! Just
you wait. Next year's chocolate is
gonna make this year's taste like a
dry biscuit!
148:
Um. I'll be hiring a normal chef next
year.
152:
What? Don't look at me like that!
What did you expect me to do?
156:
Lilie, you have to understand...
Monster Cuisine is the key to the
future...
161:
When the heck did YOU reach
enlightenment?

Hello? Guys? Do you REALLY want a
future where we're all slurping
tentacles?
172:
I'm so excited, Parfait. I've got a ton
to learn from you.
178:
With that passion, we'll have you
cookin' like a true Monster Chef in no
time!
